Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.39,0:00:59.75,OPC1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}为何我们相会于此？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.76,0:01:03.02,OPC1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}单纯的数字是无法证明的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.09,0:01:06.70,OPC1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}能让一切历史黯然无色的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.75,0:01:09.13,OPC1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}神秘大发现
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.25,0:01:12.91,OPC1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}恰巧合适的 启示的密码
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.94,0:01:16.08,OPC1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}那是宇宙级的交感
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.12,0:01:23.93,OPC1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}你能听见创造新纪元的胎动吗…？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.04,0:01:25.51,OPC1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}Burning through the sky
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.57,0:01:30.29,OPC1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}创造出至高的未来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.37,0:01:37.20,OPC1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}乘上琥珀色的喷气飞机 向着争鸣的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.21,0:01:42.33,OPC1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}载满不成熟的梦想全力踩下油门
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.35,0:01:49.30,OPC1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}飞翔吧！一如所愿
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.27,0:01:59.27,OPC1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}Touch and go, Catch the sun!
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,=================EDJ=================
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.68,0:22:21.61,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}立ち止まらず歩いて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.72,0:22:24.82,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}星を数えるより
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.74,0:22:30.05,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}消せない絆が光るよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.34,0:22:37.49,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}夢は走りだした僕らを導いてる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.70,0:22:41.86,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}願いを込めて描く世界
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.98,0:22:47.08,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}守りたい気持ちはきっと
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.20,0:22:52.47,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}立ち向かう勇気くれるんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.68,0:22:55.70,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}まっすぐ伝えたいから
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.88,0:22:58.73,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}歌うよ　ラララ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.95,0:23:01.93,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}届けて　ラララ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.13,0:23:06.14,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\}忘れない胸の奥で輝いてる
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.15,0:23:08.57,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}君がくれた光
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.63,0:23:11.58,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}一緒に　ラララ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.61,0:23:14.55,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}願うよ　ラララ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.77,0:23:18.58,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}強く握りしめる手は暖かく
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.73,0:23:24.03,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}このままずっと離さないよ
Comment: 0,0:00:00.10,0:00:00.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,=================EDC=================
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.68,0:22:21.61,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}一意向前
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.72,0:22:24.82,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}不必计数天上星星
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.74,0:22:30.05,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}永不消失的羁绊正在绽放光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.34,0:22:37.49,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}梦想已然起步 它指引着我们
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.70,0:22:41.86,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}倾注着梦想 描绘出这个世界
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.98,0:22:47.08,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}这份想要守护什么的心意
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.20,0:22:52.47,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}定然会给我面对一切的勇气
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.68,0:22:55.70,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}因为我想直白地传达给你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.88,0:22:58.73,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}唱歌吧 啦啦啦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.95,0:23:01.93,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}接受吧 啦啦啦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.13,0:23:06.14,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}在心底发光发热 永不会被忘却的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.15,0:23:08.57,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}是你给我的希望
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.63,0:23:11.58,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}一起来 啦啦啦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.61,0:23:14.55,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}许愿吧 啦啦啦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.77,0:23:18.58,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}紧握的手儿是如此温暖
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.73,0:23:24.03,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}我永远也不会松开
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
